search_results.title: Kathryn Hunter
search_results.snippet: Aikaterini Hadjipateras known professionally as Kathryn Hunter, is a British-American actress and theatre director, known for her work in physical theatre.

search_results.title: Kathryn Hunter
search_results.snippet: Kathryn Hunter is a printmaker and mixed media artist in Baton Rouge, Louisiana. Since 2003, she has run Blackbird Letterpress, a small letterpress printshop.
